defaultFirms involved range from the very large
default, 
defaultto SMEs.
default Microbiological research 
defaultplays
default a pivotal role, as the yet-to-be-developed production processes depend on bacteria and fungi to convert sugars into useful
default chemicals.
default&#xa0;
defaultThere are 
defaulttwo
default interrelated aspects to government support 
defaultfor science in this
default 
defaultarea
default. 
